---
layout: base
title: "Gallery | Yog Chumbak Delhi"
description: "Browse our photo and video galleries showcasing yoga classes, therapeutic sessions, community events, and more at Yog Chumbak, Delhi"
permalink: "/galleries/"
---

<section class="section gallery-index-page">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h1 class="section-title">Gallery</h1>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Explore our studio, classes, and community</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery-grid">
            {% for item in galleries %}
            <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="gallery-card">
                <div class="gallery-card-image">
                    {% if item.images[0].type == 'video' %}
                        <video src="/galleries-images/{{ item.slug }}/{{ item.images[0].filename }}" muted></video>
                        <div class="play-icon">
                            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
                                <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    {% else %}
                        <img src="/galleries-images/{{ item.slug }}/{{ item.images[0].filename }}" alt="{{ item.title }}" loading="lazy">
                    {% endif %}
                    <div class="gallery-card-overlay">
                        <div class="gallery-count">{{ item.fileCount }} {{ "item" if item.fileCount == 1 else "items" }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-card-content">
                    <h2>{{ item.title }}</h2>
                    <p>{{ item.description }}</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.gallery-index-page {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    min-height: 60vh;
}

.gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
}

.gallery-card {
    display: block;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: var(--transition-speed, 0.3s ease);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
}

.gallery-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
}

.gallery-card-image {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--light-lavender, #F8F9FA);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}

.gallery-card-image img,
.gallery-card-image video {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.gallery-card:hover .gallery-card-image img,
.gallery-card:hover .gallery-card-image video {
    transform: scale(1.1);
}

.gallery-card-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.3), transparent);
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    align-items: flex-start;
}

.gallery-count {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--deep-magenta, #83247C);
}

.play-icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.gallery-card:hover .play-icon {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1);
}

.gallery-card-content {
    padding: 1.5rem;
}

.gallery-card-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--deep-magenta, #83247C);
    font-weight: 600;
}

.gallery-card-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--mid-gray, #666666);
    margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .gallery-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .gallery-card-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .gallery-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
}
</style>
